 Destructor heard the desicion. He  raised his fist in victory. He thanked 
the matrix that megatron had agreed. But he heard Kit Kat's desicion to 
attack at once and all was not yet prepared. "Kit Kat please meet me on the 
bridge so I may discuss this."

::Gabriel:: He woke up. He got a comm from destructor telling him of the 
desicion. Gabriel smilied and walked out of his chamber. He left the pred 
base and headed back to the ark. The final plan was almost complete.
